"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"2022年是DAO元年。整理了部分文档，以便中文区能对DAO有更深的了解。\\n\\n**什么是DAO？**\\n\\n《[Messari 2022年加密报告：关于DAO](https://www.theblockbeats.info/news/27895)》\\n\\n**与DAO有关的思维模型**\\n\\n我们认为分布式组织是人类文明发展的趋势，可以从《[Complexity Rising：From Human Beings to Human Civilization, a Complexity Profile](https://necsi.edu/complexity-rising-from-human-beings-to-human-civilization-a-complexity-profile)》。\\n\\nKK的《失控》有助于我们从“蜂巢思维”的角度理解DAO，来自大自然的“分形与涌现”也能让我们看到DAO的力量。2019年的一个PPT可能有帮助，“分形与涌现”在第5到第14页，不过全篇都可以看一下。\\n\\n[分布式自发社群_V0.1_20191024](https://s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/a8321ef3-0359-4b79-8f29-3871dd34450c/%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E8%87%AA%E5%8F%91%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4_V0.1_20191024.pdf?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%2F20220110%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20220110T072636Z&X-Amz-Expires=86400&X-Amz-Signature=cb153988b5fe4a4dbc09f8e1258361718adf76a1ea73b0e387ea5c545e2c4427&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&response-content-disposition=filename%20%3D%22%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%25BC%258F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258F%2591%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BE%25A4_V0.1_20191024.pdf%22&x-id=GetObject)\\n\\n**DAO与去中心化**\\n\\nVitalik在2014年对各种与DAO相关的形态进行过阐述，详见《[DAOs, DACs, DAs and More: An Incomplete Terminology Guide](https://blog.ethereum.org/2014/05/06/daos-dacs-das-and-more-an-incomplete-terminology-guide/)》\\n\\n其中，从 Architectural (de)centralization、Political (de)centralization、Logical (de)centralization对去中心化进行讨论《[The Meaning of Decentralization](https://medium.com/@VitalikButerin/the-meaning-of-decentralization-a0c92b76a274)》\\n\\n**DAO前传**\\n\\n我们会认为Bitcoin是第一个DAO，因此在2018年申请了bitcoindao.com的域名。Bitshares和Ethereum分别从探索DAO,DAC等开始，开启了BM和Vitalik传奇的一生。他们一度成为区块链世界，除中本聪之外，最为知名的两个King。\\n\\n*Bitcoin*\\n\\n《[The trust machine](https://www.economist.com/leaders/2015/10/31/the-trust-machine)》\\n\\n《[Bitcoin and the Three Laws of Robotics](https://letstalkbitcoin.com/bitcoin-and-the-three-laws-of-robotics)》\\n\\n《[DAC Revisited](https://letstalkbitcoin.com/dac-revisited)》\\n\\n*Bitshares*\\n\\n《[What is BitShares?](https://moreequalanimals.com/posts/What-is-BitShares)》\\n\\n《[BitShares as a Bank - The origin of the DAC](https://moreequalanimals.com/posts/BitShares-as-a-Bank)》\\n\\n*Ethereum*\\n\\n《[BOOTSTRAPPING A DECENTRALIZED AUTONOMOUS CORPORATION 01](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/technical/bootstrapping-a-decentralized-autonomous-corporation-part-i-1379644274)》\\n\\n《[BOOTSTRAPPING A DECENTRALIZED AUTONOMOUS CORPORATION 02](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/technical/bootstrapping-an-autonomous-decentralized-corporation-part-2-interacting-with-the-world-1379808279)》\\n\\n《[BOOTSTRAPPING A DECENTRALIZED AUTONOMOUS CORPORATION 03](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/technical/bootstrapping-a-decentralized-autonomous-corporation-part-3-identity-corp-1380073003)》\\n\\n《[DAOS ARE NOT SCARY PART 1: SELF-ENFORCING CONTRACTS AND FACTUM LAW](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/technical/daos-scary-part-1-self-enforcing-contracts-factum-law-1393297672)》\\n\\n《[DAOS ARE NOT SCARY PART 2: REDUCING BARRIERS](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/technical/daos-scary-part-1-self-enforcing-contracts-factum-law-1393297672)》\\n\\n《[ETHEREUM: A NEXT-GENERATION CRYPTOCURRENCY AND DECENTRALIZED APPLICATION PLATFORM](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/business/ethereum-next-generation-cryptocurrency-decentralized-application-platform-1390528211)》\\n\\n*其他文档*\\n\\n《[Visions, Part 1: The Value of Blockchain Technology](https://blog.ethereum.org/2015/04/13/visions-part-1-the-value-of-blockchain-technology/)》\\n\\n《[Visions, Part 2: The Problem of Trust](https://blog.ethereum.org/2015/04/13/visions-part-1-the-value-of-blockchain-technology/)》\\n\\n《[Superrationality and DAOs](https://blog.ethereum.org/2015/01/23/superrationality-daos/)》\\n\\n**Modern DAO**\\n\\n*The DAO*\\n\\nThe DAO虽然因黑客攻击而失败了，然而其在DAO的历史上留下了浓墨重彩的一笔。其白皮书《[去中心化自治组织来管理信任](https://ethfans.org/posts/the-dao-whitepaper)》\\n\\n*Venture DAO*\\n\\nThe DAO开启了DAO管理资产的先例，Moloch从创建最小化可行DAO出发，成为了一个Grant DAO，帮助了诸多Ethereum生态项目。随着DeFi夏天的到来，Venture DAO越来越多。且NFT火爆之后，Collector DAO也如雨后春笋出现。我们将这些都归类为Venture DAO。\\n\\nMoloch - 一个Venture DAO\\n\\n[DAOhaus](https://daohaus.club/) - 一个Venture DAO创建平台\\n\\nCollector DAO - [Pleasr](https://pleasr.org/) 、 [flamingodao](https://flamingodao.xyz/)\\n\\n*Guild*\\n\\nGuild伴随着GameFi的火爆而来，其中YGG是Guild里最典型的代表。YGG与Axie Infinity相辅相成，某种程度上说，Axie Infinity因YGG等Guild而成功。\\n\\n*DAO的扩散*\\n\\n随着Web3基础设施一步步成熟，以及SocialFi的萌芽，DAO会越来越多，也会越来越丰富。\\n\\n当然，我们要提几个Meme DAO，DOGE、DOGE NFT、SHIBA这几个都取得了不错的成绩。然而，ConstitutionDAO筹集了4000万+美元去竞拍宪法，让$People背后有更多价值，也更加酷，期待ConstitutionDAO社区有新的创新。\\n\\n在另外一条线，FWB点燃了Social DAO，而BanklessDAO、[DeveloperDAO](https://www.developerdao.com/zh-CN)却做了一些更棒的事情。也许，Social DAO的未来就萌芽在这几个DAO之中。《[BanklessDAO — a sample of future collaboration — part 1](https://mirror.xyz/0x21C4952BC587CFF830B8E6BF16Bd0352A97a91a7/EOedlGwLY8T2otwbOX_EbDbRGsxUMTfrFqFXWJHAN7Y)》《[FWB目录 - 一个具备颠覆性的社交产品](https://mirror.xyz/0x21C4952BC587CFF830B8E6BF16Bd0352A97a91a7/B-CAhm1fMSIQu5UsVJkWoOtFJbEYKyqIhMgJnN98F_U)》《[新DAO推荐 - Developer DAO](https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LCzuLTslDr2-VUL9CveYTQ)》\\n\\n前一久，[OpenDAO](https://www.theopendao.com/)带着Web3的探索者们，完成了一次对Opensea的突袭。这让我们想起了Sushiswap对Uniswap发起的突袭，期待[OpenDAO](https://www.theopendao.com/)社区推出有意思的产品。这开启了一系列的创新，[GasDAO](https://www.gasdao.org/)也通过与OpenDAO类似的空投，完成了社区的启动。\\n\\n[TheStakingDAO](https://www.thestakingdao.com/)也将在01月10日上线，对Ethereum2.0的质押者空投$POS，以奖励其保护区块链底层安全所做出的贡献。TheStakingDAO有更大的愿景，“Staking DAO hope to build Web3 and promote more DAOs to bootstrap based on staking”，期望他们能取得成功。\\n\\n**DAO工具及创建平台**\\n\\n*DAO创建平台*\\n\\nTim Berners Lee博士说，互联网是给每个人的礼物，“This is for everyone”。在Web3，“DAO is for everyone”，我们期待人们几分钟之内就能创建一个DAO。\\n\\n* [Colony](https://colony.io/)\\n* [DAOhaus](https://daohaus.club/)\\n* [Nutbox](https://nutbox.io/)\\n* [Aragon](https://client.aragon.org/)\\n\\n*DAO工具*\\n\\n经过数年的发展，出现了很多DAO的工具，以下是主流DAO工具：\\n\\n* POAP - 勋章\\n* Snapshot - 治理\\n* Gnosis Safe - 多签、资产管理\\n* Sablier - 流支付\\n* Klero - Justice\\n* Conoly - 创建平台\\n\\n更多DAO及DAO工具，可点击链接：\\n\\n[https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1E04NcY4kCzh8ck3ZZuxElCniyS2lWvfYV-E1AM0ugx0/edit?usp=sharing](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1E04NcY4kCzh8ck3ZZuxElCniyS2lWvfYV-E1AM0ugx0/edit?usp=sharing)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641966880,\"title\":\"DAO是什么, 以及DAO工具\"},\"digest\":\"ryLeyo6HQjEhn3bTWPsxpbmunTrRNSCeUUzEYyfvJZo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE27890A9F122c6DF6F27a6Fb92970334777016Dd\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"UNUBew2pLhXm_3A8foQdT23st_GhZDXsOY2WU6wtWJ8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"QXAqt7PoCJZCxtJTTC623kWCQgD9TBoC3Z9JCbYNVHk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"KTjFzi6BCz3alRPtBd9a9D6lgyVfi3Xjx_URHSxwY6XlIVOvXCO_5PpZR68cYys2BhvQKluwbmdWCew52y-eTA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x26bb388309a77da1cab209fd26df580e1fabf4380f47439441a308ad766c7b4d5b8e863bf4c4ad5c88df015e4b445b52bd88ae2eddf3202d6ef3cb92d80802471b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"UNUBew2pLhXm_3A8foQdT23st_GhZDXsOY2WU6wtWJ8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"QXAqt7PoCJZCxtJTTC623kWCQgD9TBoC3Z9JCbYNVHk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"G0gNaaDuz63g-SabzFQP3XwBydwoJZjN1V1Ny6m7fns\"}"